Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vodka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've found out that we failed to open the e-mail at this villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. answer me!!
