Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer me, will you, Mr. Itakura!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,( 33$)\NContact with the Black Organization\N(Pursuit Edition)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. answer me!\NI Know you're there at the villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and answer me, Mr. Itakura!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we've got no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:03:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but to hide ourselves in the blizzard and make it out the back door...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so dark in here that I was having trouble picking up the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. hey, hey?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that the electrical circuit went out because of this blizzard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't open the mail because of this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:22.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for trying to receive mail in a mountain villa like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come your answer phone's working despite the black out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well black outs are frequent in this area because it snows a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm using a phone equipped with a built-in battery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how... you found out I was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha. ha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know all about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you were keeping watch over this villa, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we weren't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as promised we're nowhere near you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:08.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More importantly, did you finish the system software?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:13.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me!\NWhat as that sound just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sound of the wind tapping on the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right,\NI SS SNOWING Yeaviy over ere 00...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. I can't use the computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate to say this, but won't you give me the info directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time and place of where\NI should hand this software over to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll say it just. once, so listen well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know that station that's under construction called Kenbashi, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fashionable station that's going to be added to the Toto Subway Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning at midnight...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come and wait in front of coin\NIocker number 0032
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iocated on the basement floor of the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to bring the system software, got that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... tomorrow s a bad day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going~to have to be:hospitalized from this evening for a health check...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know about it, don't you?\NAbout my bad heart condition
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you're trying to buy-time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you still haven't completed that software?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... it's completed all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, when is it convenient for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I'm discharged from the hospital, so about three to four days later...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.00,0:05:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. give me five days...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:37.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't wait that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Extend your hospitalization!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally got an appointment with a famous heart surgeon,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I can't move the date...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were to hand it over to you before I enter the hospital,.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be today
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the construction people will be there at daybreak
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not convenient for you guys then, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:57.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4:00 then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four hours from now at 4.00 a.m...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring the software to the place *\NI just gave you info on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four hours from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From Gunma to Tokyo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.80,0:06:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's completed you should be able to bring it with you, shouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. ..four hours from now,\NI'll take it there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, don't ambush me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I spot any of your people this entire deal if off
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you were to force this software away from me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,keep in mind that doing so may throw the method of using this software
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,into the pits of darkness forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phooey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sure a cautious fellow, just like rumor has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. four hours from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of locker number 0032 at the basement of Kenbashi Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be late...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right. I got them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. just what do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you're going to listen to them and take that software over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not listening-to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lead the conversation so that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the hand over time of the software would be rushed to 4:00 this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by sounding flustered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The news of Mr. Itakura's death may be aired when morning comes. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then this deal as well as clues about them will go down the drain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now. the jewelry robber who is at large...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fortunately. it seems that none of the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,stations are covering news about his case yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means, this is what you intended to do to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was planning to tell them to rush the hand over time to an earlier time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I receive the e-mail from them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's erase all traces of us having been here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and get out of here with your beetle. Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.93,0:07:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They maybe watching us from somewhere around this villa, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we carelessly go out just like that to the car that's parked outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they may spot us...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Vodka or any of his people were around
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they would've easily seen through my lie about the electrical circuits going out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sO that I cant use the computer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. that's why you turned on the lights to this villa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know at the least that none of his people are at a distance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where they can see the lights of the villa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If"!\NThey probably tracked this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Using some alarm system that would warn them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and specify the computer of the one they re sending the mail to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just in case the mail that they sent isn't opened by the receiver of the mail
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,part of the members of the their group will be arrested...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll confirm the contents of this software with the lap top computer in the beetle,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if it's some outrageous software that could
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,be used for a hideous crime or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to report it to the police
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and specify the place of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:54.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So they can ambush the culprits and arrest whoever shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:56.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to enter a password for this software too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:10.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the e-mail a password's been set between Mr. Itakura and those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, just make a copy of it for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do that either
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's protected with a copy guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under this condition, the police won't move!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't they always secretly armed with guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:28.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you report that there will be a deal involving guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,maybe at least two or three officers will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't even know how many those guys have on their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. with 2 only a small number on our side,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we're more likely to be biting off our own heads...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless we find out what their purpose is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and present evidence to the police as to how dangerous they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as how large their organization is,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and have the police come equipped with sufficient men,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it'll be difficult to lay our hands on them
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm... how frustrating...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We know that they're coming and yet we can't do a thing about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really. there's still a way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a bit dangerous. though...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. hey, don't tell me that you're planning to meet them directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Doc. don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're most probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a flat: after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to call a nearby service station and have them bring us over a spare tire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any service station that'll come at this time of night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well. we may as well relax and wait in the car then!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:36.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't make it in time for meeting those guys if we do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that this is God's way of telling you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to keep from taking dangerous action, Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A... car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. well. uh, we got a flat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:07.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We want to go back to Tokyo.\NBut won't you give us a lift?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoh. what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?\NWe're going in that direction anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gramps,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are you familiar with the roads around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay. gramps. you get in the front seat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the kid in the back seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to intrude on you when you were sleeping. miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I was just kind of dozing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, cool!\NThis is a foreign car, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um. is this car yours. sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've gotten tired of it and was just thinking of getting myself another car though!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because this car is really expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although he may not look it, he's the heir to a big company, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That sure was close...\NSnowy roads are dangerous after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:30.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's not rush and drive safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear something funny just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:40.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stuff that we have in the trunk probably moved...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to sweat about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't smoke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.81,0:12:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you forget that 1 hate cigarettes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry... that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, to go to Tokyo turn left there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's stopped snowing so I guess we can get there before 03:00
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why were you guys in Gunma?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you skiing with your grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds great...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Watch where you're going!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have driven in the snow after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something fishy about them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.07,0:13:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that, they're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do you think you got honked at already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you that\NI'm not good at driving on snowy roads?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car needs a tune up and hasn't got its safety check yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SO you've got to drive more carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:29.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to get a safety check for this car soon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:36.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number 2 is written on the sticker on the windshield!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the inspection'cértificate and depending on the number
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.18,0:14:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the color of the sticker'it tells you when yousre_supposed to be getting
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your next=safety check. rigt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The color is this year's color.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it's obvious that you have to get your safety check by February this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right I remember now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:00.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:03.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got a postcard saying for me to go get my safety check within this month...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. sonny. when did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sticker was covered with snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it when the on-coming car passed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the headlights shined on it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.55,0:15:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the number outside could be seen transparent from the back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was "2" because\NI saw it transparent from behind
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it was actually "5"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. t hat's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got a postcard saying that you had to go get a safety check
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,within the month of February. right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you see, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't] just tell you a while ago sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That he's a Richie Rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he leaves all the details up to others to do it for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He answered you casually but the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he's not even bothered about the date of the safety check
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you've got to turn right over there, or we won't make it to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.80,0:16:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean the kid keeps blabbing on so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's such a curious child...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:14.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well. I guess it can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay... there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way sonny...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm listening to the news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,News?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:31.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of news!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About economy picking up and the new coach of Big Osaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or about the jewelry robber who is on the run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you're still so little, yet you like news...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? Was the robber caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're still escaping somewhere in the Gunma area!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:16:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But. I'm sure they'll be arrested soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seem to have checkpoints here there and everywhere like over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,License please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agh, Officer Yamamura!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're, if I remember correctly, Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, Officer Yamamura
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:35.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this Is a checkpoint to arrest the jewelry shop robbers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are group of three wearing baseball caps!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After robbing a jewelry shop in Gunma
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they abandoned the car they made their
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,getaway with in the mountains and vanished...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But one of the three is hurt, so I don't think they got too far away yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ri ht!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we got the report,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be nearby doing some questioning
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I got to the scene of the crime
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to run into the robbers who fled out of the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:15.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I pulled out my gun and said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Freeze. freeze. or I'll shoot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:21.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the robbers refused to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I fired a warning shot towards them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:33.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And. I hit one of the robbers in the tigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.91,0:18:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-hem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.85,0:18:42.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either they had another car stashed away in the mountains before hand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:46.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or they stole a car that coincidentally passed through and are on the run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didnst you see some suspicious looking people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean people who are riding in a car that is not theirs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:02.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My car tire went flat in the mountains,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.11,0:19:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we had them give us a lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Agasa. then where is your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called the car dealer and they said they'd come get it in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I left it in the mountains with the key inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:21.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then. isn't your car in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.49,0:19:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.99,0:19:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the robbers got a hold of it and are riding it around
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,maybe you shouldn't-be bothering with us and keeping watch over that car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a yellow beetle, so it's easy to spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your voices... sound familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I donst think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. may we go now, officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh will you take that jacket you have over your lap. just in case?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:56.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you suspect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See. I haven't been shot or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful, then!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.78,0:20:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. this is the Agasa residence...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Gunma Prefectural police?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Dr. Agasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that the dealers would be picking his car up in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, leaving the car as is in the mountains may give the robbers a chance to use it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:41.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we have decided to tow it away for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So. please tell him to come and pick his car up at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. yes. I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodbye then
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:51.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what they're doing in\NGunma at this time of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet he was talked into by Shinichi again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and went sticking their noses into a criminal case or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see what thrill they find in looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,faults in others at the cost of losing sleep .
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see no fun at all in playing detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spare pair of pursuit glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:40.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're going to pick up the stuff earlier than scheduled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.87,0:21:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An hour from now. at 4:00
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.63,0:21:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The place remains unchanged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's inn front of the locker in the basement of Kenbashi Subway Station...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell Gin about this too. will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get the men ready armed with guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.95,0:22:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could've gone chicken and called the cops...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.99,0:22:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Either way, after the deal, it's good riddance with him anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.53,0:22:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were planning to get rid of him inside Kenbashi Station to begin with...
